serted by a simple pin --\n(They will say: \"But how his arms and legs are thin!\")\nDo I dare\nDisturb the universe?\nIn a minute there is time\nFor decisions and revisions which a minute will reverse.\n\nFor I have known them all already, known them all:\nHave known the evenings, mornings, afternoons,\nI have measured out my life with coffee spoons;\nI know the voices dying with a dying fall\nBeneath the music from a farther room.\nSo how should I presume?',NULL),(2403,1,'fe66643897285230:4c8f24:10355763d7f:-7ff8','2005-04-18 09:22:45',1,'What talk is this? It\'s clear that my own business bores me to death--I prefer other people\'s. Thus I hope you have not been leading a double life, pretending to be wicked and being really good all the time. That would be hypocrisy.\n\nIt\'s nice to see that Kipling knows that to love oneself is the beginning of a lifelong romance.\n\n',NULL),(2404,1,'71fdc6e2051eaf7b:d59ff0:103563c4bd4:-7fa2','2005-04-18 09:48:57',558,'ess',NULL),(2405,2,'71fdc6e2051eaf7b:d59ff0:103563c4bd4:-7f9e','2005-04-18 09:49:24',585,'man',NULL),(2406,1,'71fdc6e2051eaf7b:d59ff0:103563c4bd4:-7f8d','2005-04-18 09:49:56',588,'woman',NULL),(2407,3,'68ab4a138ed4e169:1e940a6:10355fd1c68:-8000','2005-04-18 11:46:20',1140,'gloomy man',NULL),(2416,3,'d5cd601c6178d124:eb2756:10355073670:-7f2b','2005-04-18 07:29:48',3,'Frau am Fenster (1822)',NULL),(2417,3,'d5cd601c6178d124:eb2756:10355073670:-7f2c','2005-04-18 07:29:48',3,'Ventana',NULL),(2418,1,'61ab2bea7f203694:-9dc9689:1035684bbd8:-7a03','2005-04-18 14:28:21',1511,'\n-------------------------------------\n\nTo: J. Alfred Prufrock\nCC: Joris-Karl Huysmans\n\nFirst of all, I would like to commend Msr. Huysmans on his utter lack of couth. Clearly, the years of solitary confinement and broth enemas have taken their toll. That said, I believe that it is my moral duty to inform you, J. Alfred, (which is no less of a name than J-k, though you would both benefit from the use of real words and the occasional preposition