6bc','2005-05-01 15:16:46',12216,'\n\nOLD CRONE\n\n   Well at least you\'re useful for something. Let me see.\n\nTHE YOUNG SYRIAN\n\n',NULL),(6522,1,'1c40cade8a19dcd0:1d90a6e:1039984d93f:-7641','2005-05-01 15:19:44',12437,'\n\nOLD CRONE\n\n   Well she may as well be bloody invisible as far as I\'m concerned. I\'m only short, being an old crone. Let me see!',NULL),(6523,1,'1c40cade8a19dcd0:1d90a6e:1039984d93f:-7591','2005-05-01 15:20:55',12643,'\n\nOLD CRONE\n\n   Well chance would be a bloody fine thing!',NULL),(6524,1,'1c40cade8a19dcd0:1d90a6e:1039984d93f:-7558','2005-05-01 15:21:21',12861,'\n\nTHE OLD CRONE\n\n[Peering round balcony]\n\nWait. There\'s no one there. Just someone coming up the stairs. I can only see their feet. They look like... they look like little doves!\n\n[The Old Crone falls over the balcony].\n\nEeeeeek!\n',NULL),(6525,1,'1c40cade8a19dcd0:17493f0:1039b4371d2:-7d29','2005-05-01 22:50:41',170,'\n\nOLD CRONE\n\n   Well that\'s thoughtful, isn\'t it. Not like being back in that Palace of Herod. I tell you, that Princess wanted everything bringing to her on a platter. And she\'d never thank you. Snooty cow. Still, I\'m not one to complain... Wonder what ever happened to her.',NULL),(6526,1,'1c40cade8a19dcd0:17493f0:1039b4371d2:-7fd2','2005-05-01 22:40:06',38,'OLD CRONE: Looks like a load of bloomin silliness to me. These youngters! Looks nothing like it. There was gold and blue hair for a start. Still, least there\'s no willies (pardon my French) flopping around, like in them other pictures. Mind you, I don\'t trust them little stick figures. With these lines you don\'t know where they start or begin. Wouldn\'t surprise me if the whole thing turned out to be on somebody\'s testicle. These new-fangled notions. And me an old crone!\n',NULL),(6527,1,'1c40cade8a19dcd0:17493f0:1039b4371d2:-79b6','2005-05-01 22:59:02',12,'OLD CRONE\n\n   Well it all seems a bit daft to me, that\'s all I\'m saying. And I\'m used to seeing men dressed up like peacocks. Pe