 \"flow\" (the transactional feature of computation) and \"doing away\" (a clear description of subtraction) all announce my Pappa\'s poetical theme. \n\nBut simply eliminate the mass of excess and how clearly is the result displayed!\n\nClearly, then, throughout, the theme of \"thee\" is to be read as \"three\" -- for what is being altered here is a number. Of a family of three -- Mamma, Pappa, and myself -- to a set of constituent elements -- two together, and then, an element apart -- the one -- Remainder!',NULL),(8389,3,'e390b082dad85a5f:c7423b:100907e691e:-7f9f','2004-12-01 16:20:40',11,'Fare Thee Well!',NULL),(8390,3,'e390b082dad85a5f:c7423b:100907e691e:-7f9e','2004-12-01 16:20:40',1164,'- begin --',NULL),(8391,3,'e390b082dad85a5f:c7423b:100907e691e:-7ebf','2004-12-01 16:22:15',1312,'The title is an instrument of emotional calculation.',NULL),(8392,3,'e390b082dad85a5f:c7423b:100907e691e:-7ebe','2004-12-01 16:22:15',13,'Fare Thee Well!',NULL),(8393,3,'e390b082dad85a5f:c7423b:100907e691e:-7d17','2004-12-01 16:24:41',1382,'Coleridge citation is a foil',NULL),(8394,3,'e390b082dad85a5f:c7423b:100907e691e:-7d16','2004-12-01 16:24:42',80,'But whispering tongues can poison truth;\nAnd constancy lives in realms above;\nAnd life is thorny; and youth is vain;\nAnd to be wroth with one we love,\nDoth work like madness in the brain;\n________\nBut never either found another\nTo free the hollow heart from paining -\nThey stood aloof, the scars remaining.\nLike cliffs which had been rent asunder;\nA dreary sea now flows between,\nBut neither [take]heat, nor frost, nor thunder,\nShall wholly do away, I ween,\nThe marks of that which once hath been.\"',NULL),(8395,2,'e390b082dad85a5f:c7423b:100907e691e:-7c88','2004-12-01 16:26:31',1,'Fare Thee Well!\n\"Alas! they had been friends in youth:\nBut whispering tongues can poison',NULL),(8396,2,'e390b082dad85a5f:c7423b:100907e691e:-7c86','2004-12-01 16:26:50',121,'And constancy lives in realms',NULL),(8397,2,'e390b082dad85a5f:c7423b